################################################################

# MOTIVATIONS, DECISIONS, PRINCIPLES, EMOTIONS, CONFLICTS, THEMES, MYTHS, EVENTS

################################################################

:Motivation_GovernCitySafely
a :Motivation ;
:description "To keep the city safe and steady after turmoil and to glorify it through governance."^^xsd:string .

:Motivation_TestLeadersByOffice
a :Motivation ;
:description "To evaluate a man’s heart and judgment by seeing him rule."^^xsd:string .

:MoralDecision_PrioritizeCityOverPrivateFriendship
a :MoralDecision ;
:description "To condemn leaders who put friends before the country and to prioritize the fatherland."^^xsd:string .

:MoralDecision_SpeakAgainstRuin
a :MoralDecision ;
:description "To refuse silence when trouble threatens the safety of society."^^xsd:string .

:MoralDecision_PublicDecreePrinciples
a :MoralDecision ;
:description "To issue a public decree guided by these principles of leadership, patriotism, and frank counsel."^^xsd:string .

:EthicalPrinciple_Patriotism
a :EthicalPrinciple ;
:description "The country is the common protector; true friends are fellow shipmates within the safeguarded city."^^xsd:string .

:EthicalPrinciple_FrankCounsel
a :EthicalPrinciple ;
:description "Fear-driven silence is disgraceful; a leader must speak plainly for the city’s safety."^^xsd:string .

:EthicalPrinciple_LawfulGovernance
a :EthicalPrinciple ;
:description "Leadership must be proven in rule; governance requires clear intentions and ordered principles."^^xsd:string .

:Emotion_ResolveToProtectCity
a :Emotion ;
:description "Determined confidence to protect the city, denounce cowardly rule, and uphold civic safety."^^xsd:string .

:Conflict_FriendVsFatherland
a :Conflict ;
:description "Tension between private friendship and loyalty to the country, which must come first."^^xsd:string ;
:conflictBetween :EthicalPrinciple_Patriotism, :MoralDecision_PrioritizeCityOverPrivateFriendship .

:Conflict_FearSilenceVsBestCounsel
a :Conflict ;
:description "Tension between speaking to prevent danger and remaining silent out of fear."^^xsd:string ;
:conflictBetween :EthicalPrinciple_FrankCounsel, :MoralDecision_SpeakAgainstRuin .

:Theme_CivicStabilityAfterCrisis
a :Theme ;
:description "The city, nearly wrecked by havoc, is restored and must be kept safe."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_PatriotismAbovePersonalTies
a :Theme ;
:description "Country and common safety outweigh private friendships; civic solidarity defines true friends."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_LeadershipAndLaw
a :Theme ;
:description "A leader’s character is tested in rule; clear intentions, speech, and principles govern the polis."^^xsd:string .

:Myth_ZeusAllSeeing
a :MythologicalBackground ;
:description "Zeus invoked as all-seeing witness to Creon’s declarations."^^xsd:string .

:Event_CityThreatenedByHavoc
a owl:NamedIndividual, owl:Thing ;
:description "The ship of state is threatened with wreck in a sea of havoc but returns to proper course."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_GovernCitySafely .

:Event_BrothersMutualKilling
a owl:NamedIndividual, owl:Thing ;
:description "The two brothers die on the same day, each struck by the other’s bloody hand."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_GovernCitySafely .

:Event_CreonAccession
a owl:NamedIndividual, owl:Thing ;
:description "Creon holds full power of the throne as next of kin after the brothers’ deaths."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Event_BrothersMutualKilling ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_GovernCitySafely .

