:Line_163 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 163 ; :canonicalReference "163"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_163_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Gentlemen, our ship of state, which the gods threatened to wreck in a sea of havoc, has returned to its proper course."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_163 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_CivicStabilityAfterCrisis ;
:relatedTo :Event_CityThreatenedByHavoc .

:Line_164 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 164 ; :canonicalReference "164"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_164_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "I sent messengers to summon you, out of everyone,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_164 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_TestLeadersByOffice .

:Line_165 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 165 ; :canonicalReference "165"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_165_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Since I’m quite aware that you’ve stayed loyal to Laius’ mighty throne."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_165 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw .

:Line_166 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 166 ; :canonicalReference "166"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_166_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "When Oedipus was at the helm, you were unwavering,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_166 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw .

:Line_167 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 167 ; :canonicalReference "167"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_167_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "And even now that he’s gone, you stand by that man and his children with hearts unchanged."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_167 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw .

:Line_168 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 168 ; :canonicalReference "168"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_168_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Since those two in a single day died by a double fate,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_168 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_CivicStabilityAfterCrisis ;
:relatedTo :Event_BrothersMutualKilling .

:Line_169 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 169 ; :canonicalReference "169"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_169_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Each one stuck and skewered by the other’s bloody hand,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_169 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_CivicStabilityAfterCrisis ;
:relatedTo :Event_BrothersMutualKilling .

:Line_170 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 170 ; :canonicalReference "170"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_170_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "I now wield the full power of the throne as next of kin to those fallen brothers."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_170 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_PoliticalTransitionToCreon ;
:relatedTo :Event_CreonAccession .

:Line_171 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 171 ; :canonicalReference "171"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_171_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "But you never really know the heart, mind, and soul of a man until the day you watch him rule."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_171 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_TestLeadersByOffice .

:Line_172 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 172 ; :canonicalReference "172"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_172_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "In my eyes, the worst kind of leader is the one who rules without clear intentions,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_172 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:relatedTo :EthicalPrinciple_LawfulGovernance .

:Line_173 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 173 ; :canonicalReference "173"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_173_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Who holds his tongue whenever he’s afraid—now and always, that’s the lowest kind."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_173 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:hasConflict :Conflict_FearSilenceVsBestCounsel ;
:relatedTo :EthicalPrinciple_FrankCounsel .

:Line_174 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 174 ; :canonicalReference "174"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_174_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Likewise I have nothing to say for leaders who put their friends before their country."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_174 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_PatriotismAbovePersonalTies ;
:hasConflict :Conflict_FriendVsFatherland ;
:relatedTo :MoralDecision_PrioritizeCityOverPrivateFriendship .

:Line_175 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 175 ; :canonicalReference "175"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_175_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "Be my witness, all-seeing Zeus:"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_175 ;
:referencesMyth :Myth_ZeusAllSeeing ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw .

:Line_176 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 176 ; :canonicalReference "176"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_176_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "I would never stay silent if I saw trouble threatening the safety of our society."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_176 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_CivicStabilityAfterCrisis ;
:hasConflict :Conflict_FearSilenceVsBestCounsel ;
:relatedTo :MoralDecision_SpeakAgainstRuin .

:Line_177 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 177 ; :canonicalReference "177"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_177_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "I would never make friends with my country’s enemies, for I know that she is our common protector,"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_177 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_PatriotismAbovePersonalTies ;
:relatedTo :EthicalPrinciple_Patriotism .

:Line_178 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 178 ; :canonicalReference "178"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_178_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "And that we can consider only our fellow shipmates true friends."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_178 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_PatriotismAbovePersonalTies ;
:relatedTo :EthicalPrinciple_Patriotism .

:Line_179 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 179 ; :canonicalReference "179"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_179_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "According to these principles I will glorify our city."^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_179 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:relatedTo :Motivation_GovernCitySafely .

:Line_180 a owl:NamedIndividual, :Line ; :lineNumber 180 ; :canonicalReference "180"^^xsd:string .
:TV_Line_180_en a :TranslationVariant ;
:text "With them in mind I’ve already made a public decree"^^xsd:string ;
:relatedTo :Line_180 ;
:hasTheme :Theme_LeadershipAndLaw ;
:relatedTo :MoralDecision_PublicDecreePrinciples .

